1. Your presentation outline should generally include:
Solution : B. An agenda and conclusion

2. What is important to consider when telling a story during your presentation?
Solution : A. Include characters and situations your audience will relate to

3. When creating a presentation deck, what should you try to do?
Solution : C. Make the text easy to read by using at least 24-point font

4. What should a show flow include?
Solution : D. A and B
